      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80 Supra Turbo is a masterclass in preservation, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six with its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration delivering seamless boost. The drivetrain is anchored by the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, all maintaining original tolerances. The suspension geometry remains precise with factory-spec double-wishbone components and fresh bushings. The engine bay shows zero signs of thermal fatigue, with supple vacuum lines and a pristine heat-shielding arrangement. This collector-grade example exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders and an immaculate undercarriage, representing a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized, unmodified icon of Japanese performance engineering.",
